  "remarks": "Judge at the City Court of Minsk, former judge at the Central District Court of Minsk. On 26 Oct 2011, he sentenced civil society activist Siarhei Kazakou to 10 days in jail. The way he conducted the trials was a clear violation of the Code of Criminal Procedure. He sustained the use of evidence and testimonies irrelevant to the accused.",
